== Egg Bites ==

Open plastic packaging slightly to vent. With @Turkey Sausage & Cheese Egg Bites{6} in packaging, #microwave{} until heated through, ~{40-60%seconds}.

To use a #toaster oven{}, preheat toaster oven to 350 degrees. Remove egg bite from plastic packaging and place in toaster oven. Cook until heated through, ~{5-10%minutes}.

== Burrito ==

Unwrap @Sausage, Egg & Cheese Burritos{3}; loosely rewrap and place on a #microwave-safe plate{}. Heat until warmed, rotating halfway through, ~{1.5-2.5%minutes}. Let stand ~{1%minute}. Unwrap and serve.

> For crispy burritos, follow microwave heating instructions. Remove burrito from microwave, carefully unwrap, and heat in a dry, preferably nonstick, #medium pan{} over medium-low heat, about 45 seconds per side. Use butter or oil if you like even crispier edges.

== Muffins ==

Enjoy @Banana Nut Muffins{2} and @Cinnamon Crumb Cake Muffins{2} as is!

== Belgian Waffle ==

Heat a #waffle iron{}. Add @Belgian Waffles{2} to iron. Warm for about ~{30%seconds}.

To use #toaster{} or #oven{}, heat to low. Add waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about ~{1%minute}.

To use microwave, microwave waffle for ~{20%seconds}.

== Latte ==

Serve @La Colombe Triple Lattes{7} over ice and enjoy!